* What are your plans for software setup and configuration for the devices?
This would includes remote updates and the ability for hosts to change wifi settings, via Helium's official app or otherwise. 
Our product has Wi-fi, Bluetooth and wired connections, supports Web configuration and command configuration at the same time; the software has automatic upgrade and manual upgrade options.
* Which security implementation (ECC608, TPM, TrustZone, other) are you using? 
ATECC608 
* Which LoRa chipset are you planning to use in your gateway? (We recommend you don't use the SX1301 in new designs.)
SX1302
* What is the CPU?
MT7688A
* Additional Hardware Specifications: 
Indoor:
	Core：MT7688A  580MIPS 
	RAM: DDR2 128M
	Flash: 32M 
	Encryption chip：ATECC608
	Network：10/100M
	WiFi: 150M wireless rate, AP, STA and AP+STA mixed mode, support 802.11b/g/n mode
	Bluetooth：v4.2
	Power interface：MicroUSBDC5V 2A
	Antenna gain：1.5dBi
	Antenna interface：SMA
	Dimensions：160X160X45mm
	
	Outdoor：
    Core：MT7688A 580MIPS 
	RAM: DDR2 128M
	Flash: 32M 
	Encryption chip：ATECC608
	Network：10/100M
	WiFi: 150M wireless rate, AP, STA and AP+STA mixed mode, support 802.11b/g/n mode
	Bluetooth：v4.2
	Power interface：POE 
	Antenna gain：3dBi
	Antenna interface：N head
	Dimensions：140X120X55mm


